---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Programas Internacionais | Instituto Saber Global" currentPage="programas">

<!-- Section 1: Hero -->
<section class="px-6 md:px-20 py-16 max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16 pt-32">
  <div class="flex-1 space-y-8">
    <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-tertiary-fixed text-on-tertiary-fixed-variant text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">
      Excelência Acadêmica
    </span>
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-on-surface tracking-tighter leading-[1.1]">
      Transforme sua Carreira com Títulos de <span class="text-primary italic">Peso Internacional</span>
    </h1>
    <div class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl leading-relaxed space-y-4">
      <p>
        O Instituto Saber Global, em parceria estratégica com a Universidad Del Sol (UNADES - Paraguai), oferece programas de Pós-Graduação Stricto Sensu desenhados para o profissional brasileiro que busca excelência acadêmica, flexibilidade e suporte especializado.
      </p>
      <p>
        Nossos programas são estruturados para atender aos rigorosos padrões de qualidade do Mercosul, proporcionando uma experiência multicultural e de alto impacto científico.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <a href="#mestrado-saude-publica" class="px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-container text-on-primary rounded-xl font-bold transition-all shadow-xl shadow-primary/10">
        Ver Programas
      </a>
      <a href="/contato" class="px-8 py-4 bg-surface-container-lowest text-primary rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all">
        Consultar Vagas
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1 relative">
    <div class="w-full aspect-[4/5] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
      <img alt="Campus universitário moderno" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="/images/unades.png" />
    </div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl max-w-[240px]">
      <div class="flex gap-1 text-amber-500 mb-2">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1">star</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1">star</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1">star</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1">star</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1">star</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-on-surface">+1.200 Alunos Reconhecidos no Brasil</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 2: Program Cards -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-24" id="mestrado-saude-publica">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-20">
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-on-surface mb-4">Programas de Stricto Sensu</h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Titulações internacionais com validade técnica no Mercosul.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-3xl p-8 transition-all hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/5 flex flex-col h-full">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-fixed rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">school</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Mestrado em Gestão em Saúde Pública</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-4 font-medium">Destaque: Foco em políticas públicas, epidemiologia e gestão estratégica.</p>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-8 flex-grow text-sm">Público-alvo: Gestores, médicos, enfermeiros e profissionais da área da saúde que buscam liderar processos no setor público e privado.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-lg">schedule</span>
            <span class="font-medium text-on-surface">Duração Média: 24 meses</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-lg">language</span>
            <span class="font-medium text-on-surface">Modalidade: EAD / Híbrido<br/><span class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant font-normal">(conforme cronograma)</span></span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contato" class="w-full py-4 rounded-xl border-2 border-primary/10 text-primary font-bold hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all text-center block">
          Ver Detalhes do Edital
        </a>
      </div>
      <div id="doutorados" class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-3xl p-8 transition-all hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/5 flex flex-col h-full">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-tertiary-fixed rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary text-3xl">history_edu</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Doutorado Internacional <br/><span class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant font-normal">(Consultar Áreas)</span></h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-4 font-medium">Diferencial: Orientação acadêmica próxima e suporte para a qualificação da tese.</p>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-8 flex-grow text-sm">Objetivo: Formação de pesquisadores e docentes de alto nível para a produção de conhecimento original e inovador.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-lg">schedule</span>
            <span class="font-medium text-on-surface">Duração Média: 36 a 48 meses</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contato" class="w-full py-4 rounded-xl border-2 border-primary/10 text-primary font-bold hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all text-center block">
          Ver Detalhes do Edital
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 3: Diferenciais Bento Grid -->
<section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-on-surface">Diferenciais da Parceria UNADES</h2>
    <p class="text-on-surface-variant mt-4">Por que escolher o Instituto Saber Global para sua formação internacional?</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
    <div class="md:col-span-8 bg-primary text-on-primary p-10 rounded-3xl flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[320px]">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl opacity-40">support_agent</span>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Suporte em Português</h4>
        <p class="text-primary-fixed/80 leading-relaxed max-w-md">Todo o processo de matrícula e acompanhamento administrativo é realizado pelo Instituto Saber Global.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-high p-10 rounded-3xl flex flex-col justify-between">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl">calendar_month</span>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">Cronogramas Adaptados</h4>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Datas pensadas para conciliar a vida profissional no Brasil com a formação acadêmica internacional.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-4 bg-amber-100 p-10 rounded-3xl flex flex-col justify-between">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-amber-700 text-4xl">payments</span>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">Custo-Benefício</h4>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Acesso a títulos de doutor e mestre com investimentos competitivos em relação ao mercado nacional.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-8 bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 rounded-3xl flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center border border-outline-variant/20">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-5xl mb-4 block">public</span>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">Conexão Mercosul</h4>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Facilidade de trânsito acadêmico e acordos de cooperação regional.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 4: Jornada -->
<section class="py-24 bg-surface-container-highest">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-20">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-on-surface mb-20">O Caminho para o seu Título</h2>
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-0 w-full h-0.5 bg-outline-variant/30"></div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 gap-12 relative">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg z-10 border-4 border-surface-container-highest hover:border-primary transition-all">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">assignment_turned_in</span>
          </div>
          <h5 class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">1. Inscrição e Matrícula</h5>
          <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant">Assessoria completa na documentação necessária para ingresso na UNADES.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg z-10 border-4 border-surface-container-highest hover:border-primary transition-all">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">menu_book</span>
          </div>
          <h5 class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">2. Ciclo de Créditos</h5>
          <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant">Aulas teóricas e seminários avançados.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg z-10 border-4 border-surface-container-highest hover:border-primary transition-all">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">biotech</span>
          </div>
          <h5 class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">3. Pesquisa e Tese</h5>
          <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant">Desenvolvimento do trabalho científico sob orientação qualificada.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg z-10 border-4 border-surface-container-highest hover:border-primary transition-all">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">gavel</span>
          </div>
          <h5 class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">4. Defesa</h5>
          <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant">Ato acadêmico oficial para a obtenção do grau.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg z-10 border-4 border-surface-container-highest hover:border-primary transition-all">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">verified_user</span>
          </div>
          <h5 class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">5. Assessoria para Reconhecimento</h5>
          <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant">Orientações sobre os trâmites legais no Brasil via Plataforma Carolina Bori.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA Final -->
<section class="py-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-container rounded-3xl p-12 md:p-20 text-center text-on-primary relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white/5 rounded-full -mr-32 -mt-32"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-48 h-48 bg-amber-500/10 rounded-full -ml-24 -mb-24"></div>
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">Pronto para o Próximo Passo?</h2>
    <p class="text-primary-fixed/80 text-lg mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Solicite o edital completo de 2026 e receba uma consultoria gratuita com nossos especialistas em carreira acadêmica.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-6">
      <a href="/contato" class="px-10 py-5 bg-white text-primary font-bold rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center gap-3 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all shadow-xl">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">download</span>
        Baixar Edital
      </a>
      <a href="/contato" class="px-10 py-5 bg-amber-500 text-on-tertiary-fixed font-bold rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center gap-3 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all shadow-xl">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">chat_bubble</span>
        Falar com Consultor
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>
